    <div class="text-center margin">
        <h1>API</h1>
        
        <kbd>api/:channel/:user</kbd>
        <p>API for a user's logs in a channel<br>
        <ul style="list-style: none;">
            <li><b>:channel</b> - It can be a username (TenkSit) or an id (id:557479550)</li>
            <li><b>:user (Optional)</b> - It can be a username (vicesmile) or an id (id:187698721)</li>
        </ul>
        <b>Example:</b><br>
        <a target="_BLANK" href="/api/orslok/Spanixbot">https://logs.zonian.dev/api/orslok/Spanixbot</a></p>
        <a target="_BLANK" href="/api/forsen/id:117691339">https://logs.zonian.dev/api/forsen/id:11769133</a></p>

        <ul style="list-style: none;">
            <li><b>force (bool):</b> - Forces API to update the list of stored channels</li>
            <li><b>full (bool):</b> - Gets all instances where logs are available (takes longer to respond)</li>
            <li><b>plain (bool):</b> - Get the instance link in plain text</li>
            <li><b>pretty (bool):</b> - Get the links using an enhanced version of the logs</li>
        </ul>

        <h1>Redirect</h1>

        <kbd>rdr/:channel/:user</kbd>
        <p>Automatic redirection to a user's logs on a channel<br>
        <ul style="list-style: none;">
            <li><b>:channel</b> - It can be a username (NOTLUSHIN) or an id (id:410014058)</li>
            <li><b>:user (Optional)</b> - It can be a username (Drapsnatt) or an id (id:43547909)</li>
        </ul>
        <b>Example:</b><br>
        <a target="_BLANK" href="/rdr/FapParaMoar/Rubius">https://logs.zonian.dev/rdr/FapParaMoar/Rubius</a></p>
        <a target="_BLANK" href="/rdr/ZonianMidian/id:570220755">https://logs.zonian.dev/rdr/ZonianMidian/id:570220755</a></p>

        <ul style="list-style: none;">
            <li><b>forced (bool):</b> - Forces API to update the list of stored channels</li>
            <li><b>pretty (bool):</b> - Get the links using an enhanced version of the logs</li>
        </ul>

        <h1>Recent Messages</h1>

        <kbd>rm/:channel</kbd>
        <p>The most complete data of recent-messages<br>
        <ul style="list-style: none;">
            <li><b>:channel</b> - It can only be a username (AlkalineXTw)</li>
        </ul>
        <b>Example:</b><br>
        <a target="_BLANK" href="/rm/RyanPotat">https://logs.zonian.dev/rm/RyanPotat</a></p>

        <ul style="list-style: none;">
            <li><b>hide_moderation_messages (bool):</b> - Omits CLEARCHAT and CLEARMSG messages from the response</li>
            <li><b>hide_moderated_messages (bool):</b> - Omits all messages from the response that have been deleted by a CLEARCHAT or CLEARMSG message</li>
            <li><b>clearchat_to_notice (bool):</b> - Converts CLEARCHAT messages into NOTICE messages with a user-presentable message</li>
            <li><b>limit (number):</b> - Limit the number of messages returned</li>
        </ul>
